org.digijava.module.aim.helper

Class IndicatorGridItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.digijava.module.aim.helper.IndicatorGridItem

  • public class IndicatorGridItem
extends java.lang.Object
    Indicator value helper bean. Stores indicator name and both values, target, and latest actual value for one particular year. Used in reports and grids on NPD inside the IndicatorGridRow beans
    See Also:
    IndicatorGridRow
